Zimbabwe to Form Wealth Fund; own Stakes in Mines, Reuters Says

-- B y   G o r d o n   B e l l
-- 
2011-03-09T10:08:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-09/zimbabwe-to-form-wealth-fund-own-stakes-in-mines-reuters-says.html
  Zimbabwe  will start a wealth fund to
own 51 percent stakes in mining companies, Reuters reported,
citing Saviour Kasukuwere, the minister of youth empowerment and
indigenization.  The government will publish guideline on mine ownership on
March 11, the news agency cited Kasukuwere as saying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
